{"word":"G2745 - καύχημα - kaúchēma - kow'-khay-mah - Boasting","slug":"G2745","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καύχημα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kaúchēma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kow'-khay-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Boasting"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C7;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B1; - kauche&#x0304;ma</b> - <i>kow'-khay-mah</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2744\">G2744</a>; a <i>boast</i> (properly the objective; by implication the act) in a good or bad sense: - boasting, (whereof) to glory (of), glorying, rejoice (-ing)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2620\">G2620</a>, <a href=\"#/G2744\">G2744</a>, <a href=\"#/G2746\">G2746</a>"}]}